# House of Anárionath

lineofanarion1 = {
	name = An_arion

	dynasty = dynasty_anarion
	religion = faith_edain
	culture = dunedain
	dna = anarion_dna			  

	father = lineofelendil
	mother = wifeofelendil	

	diplomacy = 4
	martial = 12
	stewardship = 10
	intrigue = 4
	learning = 8

	
	trait = education_stewardship_4
	trait = architect
	trait = unyielding_defender
	trait = calm
	trait = brave
	trait = temperate
	trait = born_on_numenor

	trait = blood_of_numenor_10
	3811.2.12 = {
		birth = yes
	}
	3862.6.6 = {
		add_spouse = wifeofanarion
	}
	3912.1.1 = { #Gondor is established
		effect = {
			set_realm_capital = title:c_osgiliath
			title:e_gondor = {
				set_capital_county = title:c_osgiliath
			}
		}
	}
	4032.4.17 = {
		death = { death_reason = death_battle }
	}
}

		}

				type = married

				}
			}
		}	     				
	}
	7020.1.1 = {
		effect = {
			create_character_memory = {
				type = first_born			
				participants = {
					child = character:dolamroth28
				}
			}
		}				
	}

	7023.1.1 = {
		effect = {
			create_character_memory = {
				type = child_born			
				participants = {
					child = character:dolamroth29
				}
			}
		}
	}

	7027.1.1 = {
		effect = {
			create_character_memory = {
				type = child_born

				}

				}
			}
		}

	name = Telemnar

    dynasty = dynasty_gilthol
    religion = faith_edain
	culture = belfalathrim
	dna = lotr_vanity_sol
	
	father = linegilthol3

	trait = just
	trait = temperate
	trait = compassionate
	trait = loyal
	
    diplomacy = 5
    martial = 7
    stewardship = 7
    intrigue = 3
    learning = 6
    prowess = 10

    trait = education_martial_3


	trait = blood_of_numenor_1
    7010.11.3 = {
        birth = yes
		effect = {
			learn_language = language_sindarin
		}
    }
	
	7028.6.12 = {
        give_nickname = nick_the_sunsword
		employer = dolamroth24
		set_relation_friend = { reason = friend_generic_history target = character:lineofchief9 }
        effect = {
            add_character_flag = {
                flag = had_nickname_event
            }
			add_trait = lifestyle_blademaster
			add_trait_xp = {
				trait = lifestyle_blademaster
				value = 90
			}
        }
    }
	
	7031.5.3 = {
		add_spouse = linedurthoron23
		set_relation_soulmate = character:linedurthoron23
	}
	
	7031.6.18 = {
		effect = {
			create_character_memory = {
				type = first_born			
				participants = {
					child = character:linegilthol5
				}
			}
		}
	}
	
	7115.2.1 = {
        death = { death_reason = death_hunting_accident }
    }
}
